text: AEW St. Patrick's Day Slam is a series of professional wrestling events made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). The event started in 2021 and is usually held in March as their St. Patrick's Day special. The events air as special episodes of AEW's television shows Dynamite and Rampage. St. Patrick's Day Slam was first announced on March 10, 2021. ==Dates and venues== Event Date City Venue Main event St. Patrick's Day Slam (2021) Dynamite: March 11, 2021 Jacksonville, Florida Daily's Place Dr. Britt Baker, D.M.D vs. Thunder Rosa in an Unsanctioned Lights Out match. St. Patrick's Day Slam (2022) Dynamite: March 16, 2022 San Antonio, Texas Freeman Coliseum Thunder Rosa vs. Dr. Britt Baker, D.M.D. (c) in a Steel Cage match for the AEW Women's World Championship. St. Patrick's Day Slam (2023) Rampage: March 15, 2023 Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada Canada Life Centre Daniel Garcia vs. Brody King. == References == Category:AEW St. Patrick's Day Slam Category:2021 establishments in the United States
